          },
          "datePublished": "2023-01-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It's been 2 years, my daughters are studying in The Millennium School, Noida Sector 119. They are in class II. It's been a fantastic experience and we can see the difference in our daughters in terms of enhanced skills, learning of new concepts, confident Whilst speaking and sharing their thoughts and above all making new friends. School teachers and leadership team is doing a fab job. The way they managed studies during pandemic was incredible and even after pandemic, we are happy with in school safety measures. Time to time, different fests school has organized - Innovation fest, Cultural fest. Brilliant arrangement. I would highly recommend TMS 119 basis upon my wonderful experience..",
